# 🍫 Awesome Chocolates Report

This report visualizes chocolate sales performance across regions, products, and time periods using Power BI.

## 📁 Files
- `Awesome Chocolates.pbix` – Power BI dashboard file.

## 🔍 Key Insights
- Top-performing regions and products
- Monthly sales trends
- Revenue breakdown by category

## 📥 How to Use
1. Download the `.pbix` file.
2. Open in Power BI Desktop.
3. Explore the visuals to gain business insights.

